|text =
:'''Robin:''' (Trailblazer), are you still on Penacony?
:'''Robin:''' I have a favor to ask...
:{Choice} Do tell.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I am
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What is it?
:{Choice} Not there right now.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm not there right now
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Wait for me to return if it's not urgent
:'''Robin:''' Ah, actually... it's about the Grand Theater
:'''Robin:''' You may have heard about the Oak Family's past proclamation that guests will be absolutely safe &mdash; that is all thanks to Order's power
:'''Robin:''' But this strength has since almost dissipated on Penacony, which also means that in the present dreams, "death" is not an impossibility
:'''Robin:''' When my older brother and I crashed onto the land back then, I was thrust into unconscious darkness... But when I awoke, I was surrounded by nurses, and my brother was nowhere to be seen
:'''Robin:''' I wanted to know if he was safe, but they refused to tell me... It is out of desperation that I would ask you if you could look for my brother in the Grand Theater
:'''Robin:''' Even a tiny clue would be assuring
:'''Robin:''' I'm now, really
:'''Robin:''' really afraid
:{Choice} Don't worry. Leave it to me.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Understood
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Leave it to me. I'll think of something
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm sure he's fine
:{Choice} Prepare for the worst...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Got it. I'll help
::'''(Trailblazer):''' But I can't guarantee results
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You'll have to prepare for the worst...
:'''Robin:''' ...
:'''Robin:''' Thank you, (Trailblazer).
:'''Robin:''' I'm eternally thankful
:'''Robin:''' If you find anything, look for me near the ticketing booth
:'''Robin:''' I'll be disguised as an Intellitron dressed in blue formal attire, to avoid the Hounds' noses
:'''Robin:''' Please...
