===(Trailblazer), do you think......===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Robin:''' (Trailblazer), do you think... a bird with broken wings still has a chance to fly?
:{Choice} There's hope as long as it's alive
::'''(Trailblazer):''' There's hope as long as it's alive
::'''Robin:''' Yes, your thought echoes mine
::'''Robin:''' I saw a little bird with one of its wings broken on the panorama floor a few days ago. My heart went out to it
:{Choice} Hard to say
::'''(Trailblazer):''' It's hard to say. I need to look at it in more detail
::'''Robin:''' Is that so... You are not wrong to think that way. After all, fate isn't predetermined, and a brief occurrence doesn't shape the future
::{Choice} Did something happen?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Did something happen?
::'''Robin:''' I saw a little bird with a broken wing on the panorama floor a few days ago. My heart went out to it
:'''Robin:''' I brought it back home, hoping it would make a fast recovery
:'''Robin:''' Has my brother told you the story of a little Charmony Dove?
:'''Robin:''' That poor Charmony Dove formed a big part of our childhood and taught us about "making choices" for the first time
:{Choice} I remember the story
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I remember the story. It's a tragic one
:{Choice} No recollection of it whatsoever
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I have no recollection of it whatsoever
::'''Robin:''' Don't worry about it
:'''Robin:''' Looking back now, I realize we only gave it the right to live when we were little, but we had no clue how to ensure its survival thereafter
:'''Robin:''' But then again, who can truly define the rules of life?
:'''Robin:''' Compared to the Charmony Dove which had to learn how to fly from scratch, this little bird is luckier
:'''Robin:''' Hm? Hold on
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Robin has gone offline
:{Choice} What's wrong
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What's wrong
:{Choice} Something happened to the bird?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Did something happen to the little bird?
:{Choice} I'm still waiting
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Please get back to me! I'm begging you
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend Robin has come online
:'''Robin:''' So sorry about that! I was so excited when I saw the little bird flap its wings just now, so I immediately rushed over and observed it for a while
:'''Robin:''' Seeing the little bird get better gradually fills me with joy
:'''Robin:''' It feels like I've resolved a regret from my childhood
:{Choice} I'll remember this
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll remember this day! Truly a memorable one
::'''Robin:''' Thank you! Without your encouraging words, I'm afraid I would have stopped believing in the little bird's recovery already
:{Choice} The bird seems happy too
::'''(Trailblazer):''' The bird seems happy too. Perhaps, it has its own wishes too
::'''Robin:''' Indeed, I hope the little bird can fly high again. Thanks for your words of encouragement, (Trailblazer)
:'''Robin:''' I've got to go take care of this little bird now
:'''Robin:''' Just wait for my good news~
:'''Robin:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 03.png|80px]]
}}
